t: The story of the breton shirt
s: After the First World War, the Breton striped shirt became a fashion icon. Worn by many celebrities from the world of fashion and cinema, the Breton striped shirt became a chic, geometric and even eccentric icon in the 1950s when fashion designers began to use it.
